nodes.text: This shipping company operated in the New Mandalorian capital city of Sundari on Mandalore during the Clone Wars.

The company had offices near the docks on the surface of Sundari's exterior habitat bubble.
Siddiq was an employee at the company, working as an importer of goods. A Moogan smuggling ring made a deal with him to distribute their wares across the planet. This inadvertently led to the poisoning of many New Mandalorian children.
